<i>(Can'ter) By the way,
you spelt the title slightly wrong.</i>

01:35:06.937 --> 01:35:09.815
<i>- There's no Win Rambo.
- (Will) Oh. OK.</i>

01:35:09.898 --> 01:35:12.067
<i>(Can'ter) It was still good, though.</i>
